    <content>&lt;P&gt;We are using the S4/HANA standard PR workflow for PR release (WS00000038) with 3-level approval. The first person creates and releases the PR. At that time, an email notification is sent to the second approver. However, when the second approval agent releases the PR, the email notification is not received by the third approval agent. I have already checked that email addresses are assigned for all three agents. We send email notifications through the RSWUWFML2 program with the variant below.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Requisition release Task - TS00007986&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Please let me know What Should i further check ?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="TSG_0-1715777776109.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/111024iB7C906E9E64D764B/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="TSG_0-1715777776109.png" alt="TSG_0-1715777776109.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
